DB_USERNAME=
DB_PASSWORD=

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_BOT_USERNAME=
TELEGRAM_CHANNEL=
TELEGRAM_OWNER_ID=

4. Get your Telegram user ID by messaging @userinfobot
5. Add your bot as admin to your Telegram channel

## Run

```cmd
mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run
```

## Usage

- `/start` - authenticate
- Send any text - queues it for posting

Scheduler posts pending messages to the configured channel every 60 seconds.